name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SERP Help - Extract SERP Data Easily

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A multi purpose Chrome extention for SEO professionals.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SERP Help is a free plugin that enhances your day-to-day SEO tasks with an array of tools. By using our extension, you can extract information from SERPs, Google Auto Prompt Suggestions, and web pages.
 
Here's how SERP help simplifies everyday SEO work:

1) Autosuggest Extractor:

Search engine auto suggest keywords can be extracted one by one or in bulk. You can save these keywords into a bucket before you copy them to the clipboard. You can also clear the bucket. Currently supports Google search.
 
If you have any questions, comments or suggestions, contact us at swaraj@accustra.com
 
We do not store this information and will not disclose it.
General terms and conditions: https://serphelp.com/terms
Toolbar privacy policy: https://serphelp.com/toolbar-policy
